---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import type { AboutProps, HeroProps } from "@types";

type Props = AboutProps & Pick<HeroProps, "name">;

const { description, image, name } = Astro.props;
---

<section id="about" class="py-24 bg-white scroll-mt-24">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-20">
    
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-[#1e293b] text-4xl font-bold mb-2">Sobre Mim</h2>
      <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#8b31ff] to-[#3b82f6] mx-auto"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
      
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <p class="text-[#64748b] text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Seja muito bem-vindo(a) ao meu portfólio. Conheça um pouco da minha trajetória:
        </p>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#8b31ff] to-[#3b82f6] rounded-3xl p-10 text-center shadow-xl shadow-blue-500/20">
          <span class="text-white text-6xl font-bold block mb-2">10+</span>
          <span class="text-white/90 text-xl font-medium">Anos de Experiência</span>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-6 text-[#64748b] leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            {description}
          </p>
          <p>
            Atualmente, foco na evolução constante das minhas habilidades técnicas para entregar soluções que não apenas organizam informações, mas geram valor concreto e inovação para o negócio.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg shadow-slate-200/60 border border-slate-50 text-center flex flex-col items-center">
          <div class="text-[#8b31ff] mb-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-10 h-10">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 18 9 11.25l4.5 4.5L21.75 7.5M21.75 12V7.5H17.25" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-[#1e293b] font-bold mb-3">Business Intelligence</h3>
          <p class="text-[#64748b] text-sm leading-relaxed">Desenvolvimento de soluções de BI para apoiar decisões estratégicas</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg shadow-slate-200/60 border border-slate-50 text-center flex flex-col items-center">
          <div class="text-[#3b82f6] mb-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-10 h-10">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M20.25 6.375c0 2.278-3.694 4.125-8.25 4.125S3.75 8.653 3.75 6.375m16.5 0c0-2.278-3.694-4.125-8.25-4.125S3.75 4.097 3.75 6.375m16.5 0v11.25c0 2.278-3.694 4.125-8.25 4.125s-8.25-1.847-8.25-4.125V6.375m16.5 0v3.75m-16.5-3.75v3.75m16.5 0v3.75C20.25 16.128 16.556 17.975 12 17.975s-8.25-1.847-8.25-4.125v-3.75m16.5 0v3.75" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-[#1e293b] font-bold mb-3">Análise de Dados</h3>
          <p class="text-[#64748b] text-sm leading-relaxed">Transformação de dados brutos em insights valiosos para o negócio</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg shadow-slate-200/60 border border-slate-50 text-center flex flex-col items-center">
          <div class="text-[#22c55e] mb-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-10 h-10">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 13.125C3 12.504 3.504 12 4.125 12h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v6.75C7.5 20.496 6.996 21 6.375 21h-2.25A1.125 1.125 0 0 1 3 19.875v-6.75ZM9.75 8.625c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v11.25c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.125-1.125V8.625ZM16.5 4.125c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25C20.496 3 21 3.504 21 4.125v15.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.125-1.125V4.125Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-[#1e293b] font-bold mb-3">Dashboards</h3>
          <p class="text-[#64748b] text-sm leading-relaxed">Criação de painéis interativos e visualizações impactantes</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg shadow-slate-200/60 border border-slate-50 text-center flex flex-col items-center">
          <div class="text-[#f59e0b] mb-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-10 h-10">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M18 18.72a9.094 9.094 0 0 0 3.741-.479 3 3 0 0 0-4.682-2.72m.94 3.198.001.031c0 .225-.012.447-.037.666A11.944 11.944 0 0 1 12 21c-2.17 0-4.207-.576-5.963-1.584A6.062 6.062 0 0 1 6 18.719m12 0a5.971 5.971 0 0 0-.941-3.197m0 0A5.995 5.995 0 0 0 12 12.75a5.995 5.995 0 0 0-5.058 2.772m0 0a5.97 5.971 0 0 0-.94 3.197M15 6.75a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Zm6 3a2.25 2.25 0 1 1-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 0 1 4.5 0Zm-13.5 0a2.25 2.25 0 1 1-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 0 1 4.5 0Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-[#1e293b] font-bold mb-3">Consultoria</h3>
          <p class="text-[#64748b] text-sm leading-relaxed">Orientação estratégica em projetos de dados e analytics</p>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
